{"tid":750064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國 3D 打印槍械藍圖合法化　市民可在家打印槍械","createTime":"2018-07-20T14:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T23:41:04.000Z","uid":48066,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"41db609b8b3c4d842dccd817a98c3e8dcbdec473","tid":750064,"uid":48066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"咁。樣。仲。得。了？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n數年前提倡 3D 槍械合法化的 Defense Distributed 曾與政府因 3D 打印槍械是否的合法問題對薄公堂。長達 3 年的官司在最近有結果，開源槍械取得勝訴。在 Defense Distributed 的網站回復運作之後，最快由 8 月 1 日開始，市民便可以合法地在網上下載 3D 打印的槍械設計藍圖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/dims-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fdims-2.jpg&h=04c5d42d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 2013 年， Defense Distributed 的創辦人 Cody Wilson 被政府要求從他們的 DEFCAD 網站拿下部分 3D 打印的槍械藍圖。 理由是他們違反了國際武器貿易條例（ITAR）。當局解釋，該公司曾被下載過 10 萬次的「Liberator」(解放者) 手槍是「出口產品」，因此按法律不能在美國國內發佈。其後，Defense Distributed 聯同美國憲法第二修正案基金會（SAF）控告美國國務院踐踏言論自由。三年後的今天，政府已批准 3D 打印槍械藍圖（如 Ghost Gunner 相關檔案與 CAD 檔案）可向公眾公開。這意味着在 8 月，在 Cody Wilson 恢復 DEFCAD 網站運作後，市民便可以合法地下載 3D 打印槍械的藍圖。消息指美國政府正嘗試用不同途徑上訴，但這無疑會為其他 3D 槍械打印還未合法化的國家設下先例<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/07/20/legalized3dgunprinting/fun-tech/?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=fbnew-20c&amp;utm_campaign=unwire.hk+auto+boost+post+Engaged+20+comments+1102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2Flegalized3dgunprinting%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dfbnew-20c%26utm_campaign%3Dunwire.hk%2Bauto%2Bboost%2Bpost%2BEngaged%2B20%2Bcomments%2B1102&d=2Ff9JbElw05XPoJfiLQ2XjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=fcb5f5e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/07/20/legalized3dgunprinting/fun-tech/?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=fbnew-20c&amp;utm_campaign=unwire.hk+auto+boost+post+Engaged+20+comments+1102</a>"},{"pid":"6e34e6cef4ad8a9bec186c32644b9e122721250a","tid":750064,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:27:13.000Z","msg":"想打印女朋友"},{"pid":"a27da9b008362c9514ac8dc613a0255f1c34f062","tid":750064,"uid":103936,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"3D打印得出多數都好流<br />\n分分鐘手槍都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe0aa7ea341fcb2bd0c27366bc26a4976edca79","tid":750064,"uid":22566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a27da9b008362c9514ac8dc613a0255f1c34f062","tid":750064,"uid":103936,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"3D打印得出多數都好流<br />\n分分鐘手槍都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:34:33.000Z","msg":"試下丫喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edeccbb022916ebe95f071d44df46b6498d192e","tid":750064,"uid":103936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cbe0aa7ea341fcb2bd0c27366bc26a4976edca79","tid":750064,"uid":22566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a27da9b008362c9514ac8dc613a0255f1c34f062","tid":750064,"uid":103936,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"3D打印得出多數都好流<br />\n分分鐘手槍都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:34:33.000Z","msg":"試下丫喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:40:28.000Z","msg":"每件parts 有少少errors<br />\n成枝槍砌埋就差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3D print 有咁高品質 軍火商唔洗撈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a723b88d3d65ecd5841d16650f22c2b34a84f764","tid":750064,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9edeccbb022916ebe95f071d4